**Post Office Recurring Deposit (RD)** offers 6.7% p.a. interest with quarterly compounding (Q1 FY 2026-27). The minimum monthly deposit is ₹100 (in multiples of ₹10), with no upper limit. The tenure is 5 years. Unlike bank RDs, Post Office RDs are backed by the Government of India and offer sovereign safety with guaranteed returns.
